---
---
<section class="py-40 px-6 border-t relative overflow-hidden border-zinc-200/50 bg-zinc-50/50" id="contact">
  <!-- Ambient glow -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-5xl h-[30rem] blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none z-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-zinc-200/60 to-transparent animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 5s;"></div>
  <!-- Dot grid -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, #a1a1aa 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 24px 24px;"></div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center flex flex-col items-center relative z-10 group">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight text-zinc-950">
      Let's Talk About What You're Working Around
    </h2>
    <p class="text-base mb-12 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:text-zinc-600">
      If there's a process in your organization that relies on a workaround — a spreadsheet, a manual step, a tool that only partially fits — that is the right place to start. Send us a description of the problem. We'll respond with an honest assessment of what a custom solution would involve.
    </p>

    <div class="relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-900 rounded-full blur-md opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity duration-500 group-hover:animate-pulse"></div>
      <a href="mailto:hello@pixelcraft.dev" class="relative inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 bg-zinc-950 text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 hover:scale-[1.05] active:scale-[0.98] shadow-xl">
        <iconify-icon icon="solar:letter-linear" class="text-lg" style="stroke-width: 1.5;"></iconify-icon>
        hello@pixelcraft.dev
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="py-8 px-6 border-t text-center border-zinc-200/50 relative z-10 bg-white">
  <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400 font-medium tracking-wide uppercase flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
    © 2024 Pixelcraft <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-zinc-300"></span> All rights reserved.
  </p>
</footer>
